Package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.model.annotations

Annotation Type BoundField

  • @Documented
@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(FIELD)
public @interface BoundField
    Identifies that the annotation target is a bound property that references a Metaschema field.

    For XML serialization, the useName() identifies the name of the element to use and the namespace() identifies the namespace of this element.

    For JSON and YAML serializations, the useName() identifies the property/item name to use.

    • Element Detail

      • useName

        String useName
        The model name to use for singleton values. This name will be used for associated XML elements.

        If the value is "##default", then element name is derived from the JavaBean property name.

        Returns:
        the name
        Default:
        "##default"

      • namespace

        String namespace

        the namespace
        Default:
